-- Saudi Bank Credit to Private Sector in May Increased 0.4% to $200 Billion
-- Arif Sharif
-- 2010-06-27T12:19:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-27/saudi-bank-credit-to-private-sector-in-may-increased-0-4-to-200-billion.html

          
          
             Saudi Arabian bank credit to the
private sector rose 0.4 percent in May from April to 753.4
billion riyals ($200 billion), the Saudi Arabian Monetary Agency
said in its monthly statistical bulletin today.  
 Bank claims on the private sector increased 2.6 percent in
the year through May, data posted on the SAMA website showed
today.  
